## Description {#details}

Custom traits to do nothing on deletion.

Specialize <a href="/docs/api/structs/llvm/ilist-alloc-traits">ilist&#95;alloc&#95;traits</a> to inherit from this to disable the non-intrusive deletion in iplist (which implies ownership).

If you want purely intrusive semantics with no callbacks, consider using <em><a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/simple-ilist">simple&#95;ilist</a></em> instead.
